      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know u aren't a doctor but u sound like u know a lot. i really dont want to go to the er, it's so expensive and i'm pretty sure it's just something i ate. if i just take a high dose of ibuprofen, like 800mg, wouldn't that just settle the inflammation so i can sleep? it's not like i'm in massive pain right now, just a constant ache.",
